'From Squeak3.8gamma of ''24 November 2004'' [latest update: #6497] on 9 January 2005 at 12:19:42 am'!"Change Set:		GlobalFlapsFix-hptDate:			28 December 2004Author:			Hernan TylimPer ScottWallace suggestion this .cs only does:	Preferences okToReinitializeFlaps ifTrue: [Flaps reinstateDefaultFlaps]"!"Postscript:"| w h |Preferences okToReinitializeFlaps ifTrue: [Flaps reinstateDefaultFlaps].{ Flaps globalFlapTab: #Tools. Flaps globalFlapTab: #Squeak }	do: [:aFlap | 		w _ (aFlap referent submorphs detectMax: [:ea | ea width]) width.		aFlap referent width: (w + aFlap width)].{ Flaps globalFlapTab: #Widgets. Flaps globalFlapTab: #Supplies }	do: [:aFlap | 		h _ (aFlap referent submorphs detectMax: [:ea | ea height]) height.		aFlap referent height: (h + aFlap height)].!